Gyamfi Kyeremeh (amụrụ na 9 Machị 1995) bụ onye Belgium na-agba bọọlụ, onye na-agbachitere Oldham Athletic A.F.C
Kyeremeh mere mpụta mbụ ọkachamara ya na 30 August 2014 na egwuregwu Belgian Pro League maka Waasland-Beveren megide Lierse S.K.
N'afọ 2015, ọ sonyeere otu egwuregwu nke Eintracht Braunschweig nke Germany na Regionalliga Nord.
N'ọnwa Ọgọstụ 2017, Kyeremeh bịanyere aka na nkwekọrịta afọ abụọ na nhọrọ nke atọ na Oldham Athletic A.F.C
